Class SortedArrayList

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable, Collection, List, RandomAccess
public class SortedArrayList
extends ArrayList

An extension of ArrayList that insures that all of the items added are sorted. A binary search method has been added to provide a quick way to auto sort this Collection. The method call for this search has been made public so that this Collection can be searched. Note: Not all methods for adding and removing elements are supported.

Author:
Sean T. Treat
See Also:
